      "props": {
        "variant": "note",
        "title": "Implementation Pattern",
        "body": "Content stored as JSON in version control (same as app code). Zod schemas validate structure. Shared block components render consistently. Server-only accessors provide clean API. No database needed—files are the database."
      }
